1
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:15,599
I'm taking you for hotpot today.

2
00:00:15,599 --> 00:00:15,960
Sure.

3
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:19,039
Pay me back!

4
00:00:20,679 --> 00:00:21,399
What are you doing?

5
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,719
Give me my money!

6
00:00:22,719 --> 00:00:23,480
What money?

7
00:00:23,719 --> 00:00:24,320
Are you okay?

8
00:00:25,239 --> 00:00:25,920
Who is this guy?

9
00:00:26,399 --> 00:00:27,280
No idea.

10
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:29,039
Lunatic. He's crazy for money.

11
00:00:29,280 --> 00:00:29,839
Xiaojun!

12
00:00:32,039 --> 00:00:32,960
Give me my money!

13
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:33,840
Let's go. Ignore him.

14
00:00:35,039 --> 00:00:36,159
Give me my money!

15
00:00:39,159 --> 00:00:39,920
Give me my money!

16
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:42,719
Guo Yi.

17
00:00:43,759 --> 00:00:44,880
Don't ever let me catch you again.

18
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,480
All this time,

19
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,799
I've been secretly watching you two.

20
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:13,079
I found out that bastard Chen Dahui

21
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:15,000
is living way better than me.

22
00:01:15,359 --> 00:01:17,079
Not only is he a boss now,

23
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,719
he's also got a gorgeous woman like you.

24
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:21,319
It's not fair!

25
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,079
All you want is money, right?

26
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,680
Why don't you call Chen Hui?

27
00:01:24,879 --> 00:01:25,480
He'll definitely

28
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:26,879
pay you back, principal and interest.

29
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:29,280
He destroyed my antique vase.

30
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,560
And cost me my company.

31
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:34,079
I lost my wife and kids too.

32
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:35,840
I have nothing left now.

33
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:38,959
Let me go!

34
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:40,439
I just want to see

35
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:42,640
what he looks like after losing you.

36
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,359
Let me go!

37
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:44,599
My family has a lot of money.

38
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,079
I'll give you whatever you want.

39
00:01:46,079 --> 00:01:46,959
Just let me go!

40
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:49,280
I've done my homework lately.

41
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,760
Your family's resort went bankrupt.

42
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,040
Your family is broke.

43
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:55,359
Now you just run a country inn.

44
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,359
No.

45
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:58,319
My dad left me a huge inheritance.

46
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:59,359
I'll give it all to you.

47
00:01:59,359 --> 00:02:00,760
I swear I'm not lying.

48
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:07,680
Debts should be settled with the debtor.

49
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:10,280
The one who owes me is Chen Dahui.

50
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,319
It's got nothing to do with your family.

51
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,159
You and Chen Dahui,

52
00:02:17,039 --> 00:02:18,919
neither of you are any good.

53
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,080
I'm sorry, Hui.

54
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,319
I failed to keep an eye on Siqi.

55
00:02:34,639 --> 00:02:35,599
Someone took her.

56
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:40,159
With her taken at a time like this,

57
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:42,599
our whole plan is in jeopardy now.

58
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:45,759
Hui,

59
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:46,919
it's my fault.

60
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:47,680
I'll accept any punishment.

61
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,759
Just get her back.

62
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:54,479
You're my brother.

63
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,759
You matter more than her.

64
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,280
I know what to do, Hui.

65
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,800
Someone named Guo Yi texted me.

66
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,439
Said He Siqi is in his hands.

67
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,879
Asking if I'm feeling the pain.

68
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,599
He must have a death wish.

69
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:19,879
I'll track him down.

70
00:03:19,879 --> 00:03:20,639
Find Guo Yi,

71
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,560
but keep a close eye on Bai Ruifen.

72
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,960
Don't let anyone steal the inheritance.

73
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,120
Got it, Hui.

74
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,479
She was fine yesterday.

75
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,240
Why can't I reach her now?

76
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:38,360
Sir, your fried noodles.

77
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,039
I knew it.

78
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,479
Some people are just bad luck.

79
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,639
If you can find He Siqi,

80
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:44,759
you can curse me all you want.

81
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:46,840
After the pregnant woman's incident,

82
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,719
I'm worried about Qiqi too.

83
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,400
Tell me,

84
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,759
where on earth did she go?

85
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:53,280
I'll call Captain Chu right now.

86
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:54,280
He already knows.

87
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:01,919
Hello?

88
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,840
I've got your daughter.

89
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,599
If you want her to live,

90
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:07,000
hand over ten million.

91
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:08,039
Ten million?

92
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,000
Selling me wouldn't get you that much!

93
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,759
Let me hear my daughter's voice first.

94
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:12,919
If you don't pay,

95
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,479
you can collect her corpse.

96
00:04:14,479 --> 00:04:14,960
Hello?

97
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:16,680
Ten million.

98
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,920
I'll call Chu Feng right now.

99
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,680
No.

100
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,279
If you call the police,

101
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,839
they'll definitely kill her.

102
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,040
In situations like this,

103
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:25,439
as long as you pay,

104
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:26,160
she'll be safe.

105
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,160
Honestly,

106
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,759
Li, are you in on this?

107
00:04:30,079 --> 00:04:31,680
Why are you taking the kidnapper's side?

108
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,120
Shut up!

109
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,319
You jinx!

110
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:34,519
Stop arguing!

111
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:36,519
I'll go raise the money now.

112
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:38,120
Make sure the police don't find out.

113
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,439
No one calls the cops.

114
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:41,120
Boss.

115
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,079
Boss!

116
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,480
Calm down!

117
00:04:43,959 --> 00:04:45,079
What if it's a scam?

118
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,399
Leave me alone.

119
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:48,600
Bai.

120
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,560
You'd better watch out.

121
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:51,199
Anything you're involved in

122
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,279
never ends well.

123
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:54,279
Just go clean your room.

124
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:55,439
You talk too much.

125
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:59,560
Drowning caused oxygen deprivation,

126
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,680
severely damaging the cerebral cortex.

127
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,480
She is currently in a vegetative state.

128
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,560
Whether she'll wake up

129
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,319
depends on

130
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,720
the recovery of her brain damage.

131
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:09,600
We'll monitor and adjust her treatment.

132
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,439
But the recovery timeline is uncertain.

133
00:05:11,439 --> 00:05:12,560
We hope the family

134
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,160
can cooperate with us for the long haul.

135
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,959
We just finished decorating the nursery.

136
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,560
She likes pink.

137
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,120
I like blue.

138
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,920
We even had an argument over it.

139
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,959
We ended up buying a set in each color.

140
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:29,439
We figured we'd have at least two kids,

141
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,600
so nothing would go to waste.

142
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:33,079
Her due date was next month.

143
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,160
I already took time off,

144
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,000
and brought all the parents over.

145
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:41,240
Both families

146
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:44,279
fought to care for her after the birth.

147
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,199
Mr. Cao Li,

148
00:05:46,199 --> 00:05:48,120
we deeply understand how you feel.

149
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,399
Anyone in your position

150
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:51,079
would find this hard to accept.

151
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:53,000
But please take care of yourself.

152
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,519
You have to stay strong.

153
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:55,759
Li Fang,

154
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,879
and your family,

155
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,839
both need you to take care of them.

156
00:05:59,279 --> 00:06:00,199
If you need anything going forward

157
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:01,199
from the police,

158
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,879
we'll do our best to help.

159
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,000
Thank you.

160
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,319
Are you okay?

161
00:06:14,439 --> 00:06:16,680
I should have watched her more closely.

162
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,240
I shouldn't have brought her out.

163
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,759
It's my fault.

164
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:24,240
It's my fault.

165
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:28,040
What are you doing?

166
00:06:29,079 --> 00:06:31,439
The elders at home are waiting for news.

167
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,639
I need to go back and check on them.

168
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,199
The at-fault driver, Guo Yi,

169
00:06:52,759 --> 00:06:54,040
destroyed a family just like that.

170
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:56,040
We have to find him quickly

171
00:06:56,759 --> 00:06:58,360
to give the victim's family closure.

172
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:08,399
What?

173
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:10,959
He Siqi has been kidnapped?

174
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:14,600
Sun Bo just sent word.

175
00:07:14,959 --> 00:07:17,439
He tracked He Siqi's phone signal

176
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:18,720
and found it's already switched off.

177
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,839
The last signal

178
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,279
appeared near the restaurant.

179
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:22,079
Also,

180
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:23,279
on the traffic cameras,

181
00:07:23,879 --> 00:07:25,160
we spotted a taxi.

182
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:26,240
A few hours earlier,

183
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,199
someone reported it stolen.

184
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:28,800
Although this driver used a hat

185
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,800
to cover half his face,

186
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,279
based on his physical features,

187
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,040
I believe

188
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:33,720
he's very likely Guo Yi.

189
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,160
So according to you,

190
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,360
that means

191
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,279
Guo Yi stole this taxi,

192
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:40,480
kidnapped He Siqi,

193
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:42,480
and used her to threaten Bai Ruifen,

194
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,959
extorting ten million.

195
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:45,800
Then Li Fang's accident

196
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,800
was just a coincidence.

197
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:48,120
Looking at it that way,

198
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,000
it all makes sense.

199
00:07:50,439 --> 00:07:51,439
But I just feel

200
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,480
there's more to Guo Yi.

201
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:58,000
Do you remember the antique vase incident?

202
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,480
After that incident,

203
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:02,000
Guo Yi started acting really strange.

204
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,360
I'll have Sun Bo

205
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:05,720
get the traffic surveillance footage.

206
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,920
By tracking down this stolen taxi,

207
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:10,279
we might find Guo Yi's hideout.

208
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:11,439
Let's go.

209
00:08:12,079 --> 00:08:13,199
We're going to find Bai Ruifen.

210
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,399
She's our best bet for new leads.

211
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:28,879
Where's Bai Ruifen?

212
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,680
She insisted on taking the money alone.

213
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,279
We couldn't stop her at all.

214
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,200
Don't be scared, Qiqi.

215
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,480
Mommy's here to save you.

216
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,720
If you just behave,

217
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,159
I won't hit you.

218
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,840
Kill me if you have the guts!

219
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,799
You see, I'm a man

220
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:56,200
who prefers to be reasonable.

221
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:58,480
I'll just break your legs,

222
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,960
ruin your voice,

223
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:02,799
so you can't speak.

224
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,360
If that doesn't work,

225
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,799
I'll have to gouge out your eyes.

226
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:13,759
These noodles are all soggy.

227
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:15,399
So gross.

228
00:09:15,759 --> 00:09:17,320
I only eat buckwheat noodles.

229
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,360
Can't stomach any other kind.

230
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:22,120
Do you prefer

231
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:24,240
sweet buckwheat or bitter?

232
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,240
Bitter.

233
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:33,559
My wife used to love bitter buckwheat too.

234
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:36,159
You just want that antique vase, right?

235
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,600
Chen Hui has lots of good stuff.

236
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,840
Let me go,

237
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,200
and I'll give it all to you.

238
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:43,320
No matter the value of those treasures,

239
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:45,519
they can't compare to my heirloom.

240
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:47,360
I don't want them.

241
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:49,120
But those things,

242
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:50,799
they're worth millions at least.

243
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,960
Aren't you even a little tempted?

244
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,879
You're just a foolish woman.

245
00:09:56,159 --> 00:09:58,000
If Chen Dahui were really that rich,

246
00:09:58,639 --> 00:09:59,919
would he be sweet-talking you all day?

247
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:01,600
That guy,

248
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,600
he just wants to swindle your money.

249
00:10:04,039 --> 00:10:04,679
You

250
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,720
know him well?

251
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,240
Me?

252
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,639
We're from the same hometown.

253
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:12,200
His true colors,

254
00:10:12,639 --> 00:10:13,399
nobody knows them better than me.

255
00:10:14,519 --> 00:10:15,320
That man,

256
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:17,159
he made his fortune conning women.

257
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,679
What do you think you're doing?

258
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,679
Say one word and I'll kill you.

259
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:33,440
Who is it?

260
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,720
Here for the electric bill.

261
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,000
Don't you love

262
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,559
spying on people?

263
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,519
Don't you love stalking?

264
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,360
Stop hitting me, stop!

265
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:45,519
Where's He Siqi?

266
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:47,759
Where is she?

267
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:49,519
Where? Where? Where?

268
00:10:49,679 --> 00:10:50,480
Where is she?

269
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,159
Stop hitting me!

270
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:13,759
Picking on me, huh?

271
00:11:15,519 --> 00:11:16,759
Let's see who dies first.

272
00:11:32,879 --> 00:11:33,399
Hello?

273
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:35,120
Weren't we trading by the river?

274
00:11:35,759 --> 00:11:36,600
Where are you?

275
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:38,399
Did you bring the ten million?

276
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:40,440
Where would I get ten million?

277
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:41,759
I don't even have one million.

278
00:11:41,919 --> 00:11:42,759
I've got 200,000 here.

279
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,200
That's all my savings.

280
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:47,399
Mortgage your house, car, and restaurant.

281
00:11:47,399 --> 00:11:48,399
Besides,

282
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,360
you've got an inheritance too.

283
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,480
How do you know that?

284
00:11:52,039 --> 00:11:54,120
Are you in on this with Qiqi,

285
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,639
faking a kidnapping to scam me?

286
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:56,799
I want to speak to my daughter.

287
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,720
Otherwise, you won't get a single cent.

288
00:11:58,879 --> 00:11:59,840
Behind you,

289
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,399
under the pile of rocks.

290
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,720
Go take a look.

291
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,639
Stop playing games.

292
00:12:04,879 --> 00:12:06,000
I bet you're just a scammer.

293
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:18,600
Hello?

294
00:12:18,799 --> 00:12:19,720
Where's my daughter?

295
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:20,840
What did you do to her?

296
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,320
Let her go right now!

297
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,840
Your 200,000 only buys back a bag.

298
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:27,240
If you don't bring enough next time,

299
00:12:27,519 --> 00:12:29,320
and you'll never see your daughter again.

300
00:12:29,639 --> 00:12:31,320
You bastard, get out here!

301
00:12:31,799 --> 00:12:32,720
Don't even think about calling the cops.

302
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,360
I'll be watching you every second.
